{"tid":459283,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［攻略] 打機打到上網跟住攻略打係咪男人嘅浪漫？","createTime":"2017-11-05T15:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T10:33:19.000Z","uid":73231,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"480be6edb34c87b3bd460921aa721cef98b23d73","tid":459283,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T15:36:18.000Z","msg":"星期六日大家冇嘢做咁佢就打啲PS4 RPG 咁上下嘅game<br />\n但玩五分鐘就停住嚟開個手機上網搵攻略 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話搵唔到點解個迷又怕miss咗分枝定乜裝備咁<br />\n但玩十個鐘我保守估計有四個鐘係睇緊攻略<br />\n兩個鐘去睇勁人玩真播<br />\n真係玩得四個鐘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢又好似好 enjoy 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n旁觀者覺得好傻但佢又話係咁㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16c3a2a0a3ead8377d90eee8e1aa6a4f02616f1d","tid":459283,"uid":3067,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T15:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>星期六日大家冇嘢做咁佢就打啲PS4 RPG 咁上下嘅game<br />\n但玩五分鐘就停住嚟開個手機上網搵攻略 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話搵唔到點解個迷又怕miss咗分枝定乜裝備咁<br />\n但玩十個鐘我保守估計有四個鐘係睇緊攻略<br />\n兩個鐘去睇勁人玩真播<br />\n真係玩得四個鐘到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢又好似好 enjoy 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n旁觀者覺得好傻但佢又話係咁㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n或者咁講<br />\n每個男人打機都有佢自己覺得玩得最開心既玩法 <br />\n<br />\n你男朋友覺得咁樣係 好玩 開心咪夠囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b231ee3a522d18cb3dcf1423371cbad394a4f519","tid":459283,"uid":61282,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T15:43:58.000Z","msg":"實有人會話真男人唔睇攻略<br />\n有d人中意全部靠自己唔睇攻略<br />\n亦都有d人玩game淨係玩一週目<br />\n為咗盡量唔miss嘢/行錯路都會睇吓攻略廢事要打多次先拎到<br />\n如果你逼佢唔睇攻略佢仲唔happy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要自己玩得開心啫"},{"pid":"5410ea84dc17233e0683f16d6c9e80a9cf1796cf","tid":459283,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:14:46.000Z","msg":"我都鐘意睇攻略<br />\n特別解謎成份就一定要睇<br />\n放假唔想諗野"},{"pid":"d1f0e1ee1f30becee2ae7a77eba185c821c5ff2c","tid":459283,"uid":17352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:28:01.000Z","msg":"睇攻略就好似睇說明書砌模型咁<br />\n一步一步砌完美係幾有成就感"},{"pid":"6882ca781523f0cabe28ed8ee9313cc80b6d7e81","tid":459283,"uid":114094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"睇攻略先可以確保玩齊所有設計好既野，咁仲好玩啦"},{"pid":"5380cef9f893474afe4adba2033666f3553afca4","tid":459283,"uid":46933,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:57:12.000Z","msg":"玩dark soul果類無攻略真係玩一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288cc4d832ea1b8a4816334121ed3b6402f56972","tid":459283,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:07:31.000Z","msg":"少玩RPG 淨係玩過FF3<br />\n唔睇攻略好難玩<br />\n經營 探索 育成果啲就鐘意自己慢慢試"},{"pid":"ccfb7851e4cd2e321e8351f85dbe3cfbf60409ec","tid":459283,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T23:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇攻略先可以確保玩齊所有設計好既野，咁仲好玩啦</blockquote><br />\n其實<br />\n要跟足佢咁玩<br />\n咪同睇套戲冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ab8d336b6b512c82854c0085e8c19ebad2f08e","tid":459283,"uid":103497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T23:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇攻略先可以確保玩齊所有設計好既野，咁仲好玩啦</blockquote><br />\n其實<br />\n要跟足佢咁玩<br />\n咪同睇套戲冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個好既rpg本來就可拍成一套戲"},{"pid":"2fcdcc3e85d54c02bd9acb9be814bb4945e0ca98","tid":459283,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T23:17:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇攻略先可以確保玩齊所有設計好既野，咁仲好玩啦</blockquote><br />\n其實<br />\n要跟足佢咁玩<br />\n咪同睇套戲冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個好既rpg本來就可拍成一套戲</blockquote><br />\n但好似冇乜遊戲》戲好睇喎<br />\n<br />\nSilent hills 都麻麻<br />\n拍唔返個氣氛<br />\n夾硬要加啲男角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf5184e72c300803bc24eb664d508b8fb7bc059","tid":459283,"uid":99124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T23:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇攻略先可以確保玩齊所有設計好既野，咁仲好玩啦</blockquote><br />\n其實<br />\n要跟足佢咁玩<br />\n咪同睇套戲冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個好既rpg本來就可拍成一套戲</blockquote><br />\n但係睇攻略算唔算自己劇透自己"},{"pid":"96ada6d27e66bd1e6c377a93d98cdbcdfada3a54","tid":459283,"uid":47966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T23:31:04.000Z","msg":"睇攻略玩果陣唔會有驚喜感覺"},{"pid":"6ca6d734ecc520467b252842d7aa72ad6d2e5dbd","tid":459283,"uid":92361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T00:01:09.000Z","msg":"無計...依家放工已經好累, 如果打爆機先發現唔係good ending又要玩多次我真係跳樓"},{"pid":"56992f27c18a75315c8dd174a1e91ada3dff4cfc","tid":459283,"uid":5341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T00:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇攻略先可以確保玩齊所有設計好既野，咁仲好玩啦</blockquote><br />\n其實<br />\n要跟足佢咁玩<br />\n咪同睇套戲冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一個好既rpg本來就可拍成一套戲</blockquote><br />\n但好似冇乜遊戲》戲好睇喎<br />\n<br />\nSilent hills 都麻麻<br />\n拍唔返個氣氛<br />\n夾硬要加啲男角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為一隻rpg有好多唔同支線<br />\n主角同好多唔同人交流<br />\n佢d劇情cg加埋可能都要播個幾鐘先完，咁你話改做電影邊可能好睇又完整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38f88448f0e90aca5c1497ea6ede37b2e0a22ca","tid":459283,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T00:10:35.000Z","msg":"玩牧場物語一定要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dffdbdcca705c3ac4c586e9a595f56fb6c4a66e","tid":459283,"uid":61725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T00:26:45.000Z","msg":"細個唔睇攻略點玩洛克人"},{"pid":"90173ebccea8675e01895966e1978929b5174462","tid":459283,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T00:52:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be6425c9edf5801920371cf043b9e12358d8969d","tid":459283,"uid":48381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T01:03:18.000Z","msg":"盡量唔睇就算，真係唔掂先睇攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正打機都係要開心姐，無謂去咁盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1